CREATE TABLE savethebunnies.files 
	( idFile INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT ,
	name VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL ,
	type VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL ,
	content LONGBLOB NOT NULL ,
	PRIMARY KEY (idFile)); 
CREATE TABLE savethebunnies.users
	(idUser INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT ,
	username VARCHAR(35) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
	name VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL ,
	password VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL ,
	email VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL,
	lastLevenPassedStory INT NOT NULL ,
	levelsBuilt varchar(1000) NOT NULL,
	levelsPassed varchar(1000) NOT NULL,
	imageProfile INT NOT NULL ,
	dateRegistration DATE NOT NULL,
	PRIMARY KEY (idUser),
	FOREIGN KEY (imageProfile) REFERENCES savethebunnies.files (idFile) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE); 
CREATE TABLE savethebunnies.levels
	( idLevel INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT ,
	idTxtConfig INT NOT NULL,
	idUser INT NOT NULL,
	PRIMARY KEY (idLevel),
	FOREIGN KEY (idTxtConfig) REFERENCES savethebunnies.files (idFile) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE,
	FOREIGN KEY (idUser) REFERENCES savethebunnies.users (idUser) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE);
